<plot>Based on the play by 'Joe Orton' (qv) this film follows the adventures of two pals who have pulled off a bank robbery and have to hide the loot. Fortunately (?) one of them works in a funeral parlour and they have a coffin to spare. Then there's the gold-digger nurse and the gonad-grabber detective and a host of other wonderful characters.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?341614</url></doc>
